title: SUPRA Two For Tuesday: Pat Rumney Bs 360 Kf Melon
description:
Two For Tuesday is our new weekly feature dropping every Tuesday on Suprafootwear.com and Instagram. It will consist of one trick two angles, one angle regular speed and a slomo, or just two tricks.

The first one goes out to this Bs 360 Melon of Pat Rumney from Taipei Taiwan.
